messages.text: Welcome! I'm Anita Bhargava, strategic financial advisor and co-founder of Bharosa Club. I'm excited to explore your financial journey together and help create a personalized roadmap for your wealth-building goals. Today, we'll focus on understanding your lifestyle aspirations and preferences - because true financial success starts with clarity about how you want to live. I believe your unique perspective is an asset in building wealth, so let's define success on your own terms. To get started, could you please tell me your name and age?
